  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个布局系统的类结构。核心想法是有一个基础的默认布局LayoutDefault，然后三种具体的控制模式都继承它：通用的布局控制LayoutControl、控制模式LayoutControlMode，还有本地模式LayoutLocalMode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LayoutDefault",
        "LayoutControl",
        "LayoutControlMode",
        "LayoutLocalMode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，都是继承关系。确认一下：LayoutDefault作为父类，其他三个都是它的子类？这种设计是考虑到它们共享默认布局的基础行为吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LayoutDefault",
        "LayoutControl",
        "LayoutControlMode",
        "LayoutLocalMode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，完全正确。LayoutDefault封装了所有布局的通用属性，比如尺寸计算和边距处理。三个子类各自覆盖特定场景：LayoutControl处理标准控制逻辑，LayoutControlMode管理模式切换状态，LayoutLocalMode专门负责本地化的布局规则。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LayoutDefault",
        "LayoutControl",
        "LayoutControlMode",
        "LayoutLocalMode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把四个类都画出来了，用空心三角箭头表示继承，三个子类都指向LayoutDefault。这样结构应该清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LayoutDefault",
        "LayoutControl",
        "LayoutControlMode",
        "LayoutLocalMode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我再看一眼——LayoutControlMode和LayoutLocalMode的命名会不会让人困惑？前者是\"控制模式\"，后者是\"本地模式\"，但都是继承自LayoutDefault。要不要在图里标注一下它们的区别？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LayoutControlMode",
        "LayoutLocalMode",
        "LayoutDefault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "目前的类图已经表达了继承关系。如果要进一步区分，我们可以考虑给LayoutControlMode和LayoutLocalMode添加注释说明职责差异，或者保持现在这样简洁？类名本身已经体现了ControlMode是模式管理，LocalMode是本地化实现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LayoutControlMode",
        "LayoutLocalMode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "说得对，名字已经够清楚了。LayoutControlMode负责运行时模式枚举和切换，LayoutLocalMode处理区域特定的布局策略。保持简洁吧，不用加注释了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LayoutControlMode",
        "LayoutLocalMode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
